{"tid":549740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆：高鐵營運初期或需補貼","createTime":"2018-02-04T03:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T04:48:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb10d7db1ab1394bf5ff56680ad967b19e648b2","tid":549740,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:12:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180204/20294742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180204%2F20294742&d=BAvQ12%2F47ujByeBCDDnys8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1d979db7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180204%2F20294742&h=bd5d7c32\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180204/20294742</a><br />\n<br />\n陳帆：高鐵營運初期或需補貼<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180204/large/04la6p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180204%2Flarge%2F04la6p5.jpg&h=cc99ce2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳帆估計高鐵可在約8至10年內錄到盈利。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】廣深港高鐵香港段預計今年第3季通車，運屋局局長陳帆昨指高鐵通車初期未必能收支平衡，要營辦商港鐵自行補貼營運並「唔出奇」，但料8至10年內可錄盈利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要港鐵自行拉上補下<br />\n<br />\n陳帆昨出席電台節目時指高鐵通車初期「一定要守」，要補貼營運開支並不出奇，預料香港段「10年8載都應該見到有回報」。他在節目後補充，港府與港鐵將簽署為期50年的營運協議，表明港府不會就高鐵項目，向港鐵提供營運補貼，「佢（港鐵）要喺嗰50年自負盈虧，佢自己要拉上補下，自己去畀補貼，唔係政府（提供）嘅補貼」。<br />\n<br />\n陳續指高鐵定價亦已考慮長遠營運狀況，強調高鐵財務狀況長遠仍屬健康。對於高鐵票價被質疑收費貴，車站又遠離廣州市中心，他指「唔同人有唔同選擇」，當局估算高鐵每日客量為10.9萬人次，相對本港每年陸路出入境2.2億人次旅客，估算並非過高。他有信心一地兩檢條例草案，可順利獲立法會三讀通過，估計約於今年5月完成立法程序，又期望高鐵9月尾之前可以投入服務。<br />\n<br />\n翻查港府2016年提交立法會的文件，港府當時估算高鐵投入運作初期可錄得收益平衡，首季EBITDA估算有1.5億元。一地兩檢關注組專家小組代表梁啟智撰文批評，當年政府曾經稱高鐵客量就算低於預期，出現營運虧損可能性也不大，惟陳帆昨改口風，稱高鐵最初幾年要補貼也不足為奇，代表政府在高鐵財務問題已「走數」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭啟源"},{"pid":"e2c0838211a22ae144732514b001b82365f1a7d3","tid":549740,"uid":3573,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:13:24.000Z","msg":"初佢老母咩<br />\n直頭一直都要補貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0d02813d60acfab80d3df654ff02a91458b85c","tid":549740,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"又可以貪一大筆"},{"pid":"a27fe40b55eb720fc526890cfc81564080da2dc4","tid":549740,"uid":51041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"仆你個街又一個鄭汝華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6096c6b8099ae7f04f71a04bb2b388188dd81875","tid":549740,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2c0838211a22ae144732514b001b82365f1a7d3","tid":549740,"uid":3573,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:13:24.000Z","msg":"初佢老母咩<br />\n直頭一直都要補貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:19:05.000Z","msg":"咪撚就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e33f60bf1450dbdf7ccef3fd5c8b7f25ce0f93","tid":549740,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:21:13.000Z","msg":"最初果一萬年"},{"pid":"5ae6bfba0158c6b4d4ca77296cf6e9b834ee0d1e","tid":549740,"uid":106629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T03:31:05.000Z","msg":"趕鐵無正苦補貼仲會做咩 反正建設費係正苦比 車票收入唔夠每日營運開支同你宣佈停駛 正苦有得唔科水咩<br />\n你班友唔係諗住賣車飛可以賺返個一千億返黎呀嘛? 香港車票收益得三成咋"},{"pid":"64c7a8d89e9dba751cb9ef0646e3b838c1658559","tid":549740,"ui